{
  "page": "Feature quote/167",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p>“I will not fight you, nor will I kneel to you. <a href=\"/index.php/Dorne\" title=\"Dorne\">Dorne</a> has no king. Tell your <a href=\"/index.php/Aegon_I_Targaryen\" title=\"Aegon I Targaryen\">brother</a> that.” —<a href=\"/index.php/Meria_Martell\" title=\"Meria Martell\">Meria Martell</a><br />“I shall, but we will come again, Princess, and the next time we shall come with fire and blood.” —<a href=\"/index.php/Rhaenys_Targaryen\" title=\"Rhaenys Targaryen\">Rhaenys Targaryen</a><br />“Your words. Ours are <i>Unbowed</i>, <i>Unbent</i>, <i>Unbroken</i>. You may burn us, my lady... but you will not bend us, break us, or make us bow. This is Dorne. You are not wanted here. Return at your peril.” —Meria Martell<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabaegon.27s_conquest.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabaegon.27s_conquest.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></p><div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rfabaegon.27s_conquest.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabaegon.27s_conquest.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/Fire_%26_Blood\" title=\"Fire &amp; Blood\">Fire &amp; Blood</a></i>, Aegon's Conquest.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260405023503\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.007 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.008 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 101/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 8414/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 210/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 89/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 7/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 573/5000000 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n1